Quickstrike:






Quickstrike didn't like no bot hovering behind him. It made him more nervous 
than he already was. He turned his shoulders and head around to look at 
Sinesis. "Don't get behind me. Yer makin' me nervous. If we can get someone 
t' fly me t' th' base, then maybe we can get in there an' get th' repairs we 
need."
